      "kind": "bullet",
      "text": "State Laws Privacy Policy Singapore Supplemental Privacy Page This Singapore Supplemental Privacy Page should be read in conjunction with LinkedIn’s Privacy Policy which describes LinkedIn’s practices regarding the collection, use and sharing of personal data of our members.The goal of this Page is to provide our Singapore members with information that is helpful to them in understanding the transparency and privacy settings that support LinkedIn’s compliance with Singapore’s Personal Data Protection Act.",
